Dishes of the World 2025
Embark on a global culinary adventure at "Dishes of the World       2025," a food tasting event celebrating diverse flavors and       traditions from around the globe. Experience an exquisite array of       dishes, each crafted to showcase the unique essence of its       culture. Join us for an unforgettable journey through taste,       culture, and community.

Date: 2025.01.16; 14h00-15h30;

Place: AGH University, bld. U2
